{"tid":684732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"NBA咁樣做會唔會變返競爭性大啲。。。","createTime":"2018-05-30T19:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T02:54:05.000Z","uid":173349,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5cd0bf4a89b7bf0d05fec9b352cb87386e56d3","tid":684732,"uid":173349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:27:12.000Z","msg":"取消返防守三秒<br />\n唔好下下一過左就空晒<br />\n要多啲戰術去猜散人地制造進攻機會<br />\n咁就唔會話一個球星屈機就carry成隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/032114_a739c149a1b988f73ff8420ff89c402c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F032114_a739c149a1b988f73ff8420ff89c402c.png&h=98d7563d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/032115_6c69c74a8b7a24273911c5da6df7c4d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F032115_6c69c74a8b7a24273911c5da6df7c4d3.png&h=1992ef0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似上面圖咁<br />\n明知人地單打好大機會會過你<br />\n隊友都唔可以踩定入去準備補位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣雖然係觀賞性會高啲<br />\n但係好撚失衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過無計，NBA係商業化，要造星<br />\n太少入波就無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純忽發奇想討論下，唔啱聽唔好屌太勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a88c8b3dc038514195a43a6e5d99597d4d5cfd","tid":684732,"uid":884,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:30:18.000Z","msg":"其實冇關係 如果係打5小陣容<br />\n你有條友長期防守塞死中間 變相容易左inside out到時一分返出面就比人射死"},{"pid":"16726fa6c6113cbd35b465f76b5def5ad0239709","tid":684732,"uid":173349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1a88c8b3dc038514195a43a6e5d99597d4d5cfd","ti